sentence: In early trading on Monday, shares of Intel Corp (INTC) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 1.6%.
Year to date, Intel Corp registers a 24.7% gain.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Home Depot (HD), trading down 0.5%.
Home Depot is showing a gain of 26.3% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Exxon Mobil Corp (XOM), trading down 0.5%, and Apple (AAPL), trading up 1.1% on the day.
